{"tid":121114,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"情人節我同男朋友就嚟分開","createTime":"2017-02-15T03:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T04:32:52.000Z","uid":79475,"like":0,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f276a4da89f96e5355b9c476fb20d27a555e0f9","tid":121114,"uid":79475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:34:45.000Z","msg":"今年係我地嘅第一年 尋晚我地約咗放工去食飯<br />\n我見到佢冇買花比我 我唔開心發咗佢好大嘅脾氣 一路喊<br />\n成餐飯氣氛就因為我喊而變得好差<br />\n我期待人生第一次嘅情人節比我一手破壞晒<br />\n<br />\n因為我以為淨係得我準備<br />\n我以為你冇誠意<br />\n我未收過所以睇重咗呢啲物質表達多過平時你對我嘅關心/一齊相處嘅開心<br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己好港女 冇呢啲物質野就咁樣話佢傷害佢<br />\n竟然因為呢樣野我咁樣對佢 但我真係真係好鍾意你一路以嚟為我做過嘅野<br />\n雖然唔止呢件事 呢個禮拜我地亦嘈左好多次<br />\n我明白你好想同我分擔我嘅麻煩 <br />\n但我永遠都冇同你直接講我心入面諗到嘅野 要你估要你氹<br />\n<br />\n如果可以返轉頭 我一定唔會再用呢啲方法去表達自己嘅不滿<br />\n我知道今次對你有好大嘅影響<br />\n如果我地可以好似以前咁 我今次真係會改 我知道真正要嘅野<br />\n會改左收收埋埋呢樣野<br />\n因為我真係明白如果我一日唔放開自己 唔放過佢 我地每次都只係重覆返之前嘅野<br />\n我好唔想冇咗你 我唔會再令你咁無助咁傷心<br />\n<br />\n如果你睇到嘅話 我唔係想咁多人知道我地嘅事 但我好想同你道歉<br />\n我真係知自己嘅問題 對唔住"},{"pid":"cfb9eba15e764474915043e2af7c384d39beddd9","tid":121114,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:36:09.000Z","msg":"係度講有鬼用咩<br />\n返去跪玻璃啦"},{"pid":"df97b94d66530f893f94cc2f3dd618e09bb011a0","tid":121114,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:36:15.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdf361f2305f220326329f020c396495235adbe","tid":121114,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\n無人想知"},{"pid":"a3e3ad58924cd7ca41b4a753e8d1f2cabc93fb6d","tid":121114,"uid":71453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:37:01.000Z","msg":"直接同佢講啦 唔好等無左先黎後悔"},{"pid":"4e5087dece9c3b949e2248e46863e095f6ecb512","tid":121114,"uid":46312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"比多次機會你咪又係咁<br />\n你唔會改到架啦<br />\n性格呢樣野係點就係點<br />\n<br />\n利申：自己以為改過其實冇改過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa456788afbf1b417b4bdceae9c3c267ee920a5","tid":121114,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:37:50.000Z","msg":"洗唔撚洗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6ac86ec92022764474c0892cd3699ca60642a0","tid":121114,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:39:08.000Z","msg":"基"},{"pid":"544a781cd4f443f615c4db541a25335a10457888","tid":121114,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"其實重視節日同禮物真係有點兒On9<br />\n我覺得有佢係身邊已經夠<br />\n<br />\n利申：初戀拍左8年+結婚4年"},{"pid":"7b65b6752b401b0cb0dc2e44196c01929a1e0a18","tid":121114,"uid":68981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:01:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ec6bebb8a560748c467613b330dcb406c0ae046","tid":121114,"uid":17945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:03:55.000Z","msg":"負評 上一頁"},{"pid":"10471a0ec4eca7b33b33202be91e837d9fbbab2f","tid":121114,"uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:06:22.000Z","msg":"唔洗喊呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17499346e5444ef4110d47dc11b620add82a3449","tid":121114,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"為咗無花收而大發脾氣真係好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb1240dabfd01d8c10c790531f4c9d17dc29039","tid":121114,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T04:07:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗喊呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal